{"tid":1458814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑狗會點樣應對塞爆機場？","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T19:08:15.000Z","uid":14067,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"7b16e5b6c56d2d24ebf9ddcccf32d3caec71eaf1","tid":1458814,"uid":14067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"今日算係對政府造成實際打擊<br />\n班狗應該有晒部處點應對<br />\n我地應該預先諗下點樣counter，到時係留定散大家心裡都有個底<br />\n<br />\n1. 冷處理完全唔理<br />\n<br />\n2. 放廿幾隻扮示威者既狗衝入禁區，即刻出黎清場<br />\n<br />\n3. 限制機場流量？<br />\n<br />\n知己知彼百戰百勝<br />\n光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"8ce1925e46d8cab22883f7a28b61496179b233b7","tid":1458814,"uid":14067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a28a5531f98756ad1bfe6e4cfe57ee119c24760","tid":1458814,"uid":219277,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"2係最有可能<br />\n3可以點限制?<br />\n限制左似係助攻多d"},{"pid":"111aacb13e98e6b150639c64447af3af24febed3","tid":1458814,"uid":71713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e893f08f458e656c71e9d3b9cb7e79f5d000d42b","tid":1458814,"uid":87735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"如果係2 咪起身走囉"},{"pid":"1b0954ed35f7dcc802e6b7625caeb025f8d4db4d","tid":1458814,"uid":14067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a28a5531f98756ad1bfe6e4cfe57ee119c24760","tid":1458814,"uid":219277,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"2係最有可能<br />\n3可以點限制?<br />\n限制左似係助攻多d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"我都唔知佢地做得出d咩<br />\n純粹想brain storm下<br />\n可以封青馬一邊搞到慢左入機場都好煩"},{"pid":"34808189cfba5dac7e85c5b8f77783cc615fef72","tid":1458814,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:25.000Z","msg":"萬人一推所有記者瘋狂插問追問721 811 唔俾仆街政府